{"tid":730145,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林曉峰過檔頭炮幫手執生","createTime":"2018-07-05T07:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T08:49:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b716926e7bd5baaf8100152d669ba435a00f7cbd","tid":730145,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180705/20440270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440270&d=bKO%2BRaOqStztDnSgQgnBH%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=bce5dd90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440270&h=275c21b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180705/20440270</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月05日 <br />\n<br />\n林曉峰過檔頭炮幫手執生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180705/large/05ec2p17e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F05ec2p17e.jpg&h=0c76abaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■對於網友留言撐他離開無綫，林曉峰表示喜歡工作有變化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林曉峰（Lo）上月底離開無綫後，前晚首度現身ViuTV，擔任戶外騷直播節目《Good Night Show全民睇波派對》嘉賓，跟ViuTV主持陳炳銓、強尼及陳俞希等合作，第一日開工，阿Lo與眾主持不但甚有默契，當其他主持忘記介紹唱歌環節時，他更主動執生說︰「大家不如聽吓歌先。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180705/large/05ec2p18e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F05ec2p18e.jpg&h=d3cf647b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林曉峰謙稱要與時並進，要向一班後輩主持學習。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問到ViuTV有否洽談新節目，阿Lo說：「如果佢哋問我咪傾吓，何樂而不為？不過，我又唔係正式演員，又唔係正正式式主持，又唔係DJ或歌手，係乜都鍾意做嘅人。」問他是簽演員約或純合作，他則指：「工作及家庭，我交畀經理人同太太去處理。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：馬建華<br />\n攝影：陳俊強  <br />\n<br 